  "original_title": "\u0b8a\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbe\u0bb5\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1\u0bb1\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b8e\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0baa\u0bca\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0b85\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bc8\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 \u0b95\u0bbe\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bb5\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0b89\u0baf\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0bb4\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "A man was killed while waiting for a fuel card at the police station",
      "author": "T. Saranya",
      "body_lines": [
        "A person who was waiting to get a fuel card at the Jaffna Urban Police Divisional Secretariat has suddenly fainted and died.",
        "Nadarasa Premkumar (48 years old) from Velani Puliyangkudal area has died in this incident which took place on Friday.",
        "The person in question suddenly fainted while waiting to get his fuel card at the Home Police Divisional Secretariat.",
        "After that, the bystanders rescued him and admitted him to the local police hospital, but he succumbed to his injuries."
      ],
